snippet.title: Parkitect 'Big Brother' Trailer
snippet.description:
Parkitect, the theme park builder and management sim, is coming to Steam Early Access on May 5th!
Our Steam store page is live now: http://store.steampowered.com//app/453090
Also, check out our devlog for weekly updates: http://devlog.themeparkitect.com

Site: http://themeparkitect.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ParkitectGame
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ThemeParkitect/
